{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"95108-wet-or-dry","title":"Wet or Dry","description":"What do you do with your waste? Do you have separate bins for the wet and the dry? Read this fun poem and give it a try.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Lovleen  Misra "],"illustrators":["Kavita Singh Kale"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/95108-wet-or-dry"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/145759/size3/beb14f9fe944bd7f5b8da10710b44755.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/145759/size6/beb14f9fe944bd7f5b8da10710b44755.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/145718/size6/5ded667c43208c20739d914904521e2a.jpg","text":"Separate the waste.\nYes, do try.\nA bin for wet,\na bin for dry.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/145719/size6/22120bdc92cb104bd18fab1f56ae3cf1.jpg","text":"Scoop the wet off plates and pots.\nPick up peels and scraps, left to rot.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/145720/size6/0f59b2f2b81f3cc1e05b49515fb3f223.jpg","text":"Mushy, gooey—yes, all of that.\nEven the poo\nof your dog or cat!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/145721/size6/a9124d3ce5a1877e55946f686d581723.jpg","text":"Separate the rubber, the plastic,\nPut them all in different bins.\nPaper, glass,\neven metal pins.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/140716/size6/0da63c165546c8212d7b188ef2aceb8e.jpg","text":"Separate the waste, give it a try.\nYou know what is wet, what is dry.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/145722/size6/05f0a0f69f629145f4b3a08e73f9ee73.jpg","text":"Learn to be smart with your trash.\nReuse, remove, reduce your trash.\nTime to be careful,\nnot be rash.","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/140718/size6/69ee6d9e0cfd100660818cc9ae1af414.jpg","text":"8/8","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":7,"words":93}}